-- pd.package: Admonitions
name: fifthtry.github.io/admonitions

The admonitions package(fifthtry.github.io/admonitions). Use `FTD` custom
admonitions styles for your web pages.

How to use?

-- cb.code: Add this to your FASTN.ftd
lang: ftd

\-- fastn.dependency: fifthtry.github.io/admonitions as cbox

\-- fastn.auto-import: cbox

-- pd.component: `cbox.note` Basic usage example
name: `-- cbox.note:`

Use below code snippet to use this admonitions component as cbox.

-- cb.code: How to use
lang: ftd

\-- cbox.note: Noteworthy Heading

Of all the things possible, this is what you came up with? I am disappointed in 
your lack of ingenuity.

\-- end: cbox.note

-- tf.h3: Output of above example:

-- note: Noteworthy Heading

Of all the things possible, this is what you came up with? I am disappointed in 
your lack of ingenuity.

-- end: note




